## 4. Installing Dependencies

### System Packages

```bash
sudo apt install -y \
  python3-flask \
  python3-psutil \
  sqlite3 \
  iptables \
  qrencode \
  cloudflared \
  curl
```

> **Note:** If `cloudflared` is not available via `apt`, install it manually:
> ```bash
> curl -L https://github.com/cloudflare/cloudflared/releases/latest/download/cloudflared-linux-arm64.deb -o cloudflared.deb
> sudo dpkg -i cloudflared.deb
> ```

### Python Packages

```bash
pip3 install qrcode[pil] psutil --break-system-packages
```

