## 9. Remote Admin Setup (Cloudflare Tunnel)

To access the admin panel from anywhere without port forwarding:

```bash
cd /opt/captive-portal/Project-files
python3 tunnel_mailer.py &
```

The script will:
1. Start `cloudflared` and point it at `http://127.0.0.1:<PORTAL_PORT>`
2. Parse the output for the `trycloudflare.com` URL
3. Send you an email with a direct link to `/admin`

If the tunnel crashes or disconnects, the script automatically restarts it after 10 seconds.

