## 11. First-Time Admin Access

### Local Access

```
http://192.168.50.1:8080/admin
```

### Remote Access (via Cloudflare Tunnel)

Check your email for the link — it will look like:

```
https://random-words.trycloudflare.com/admin
```

### Logging In

Enter the `ADMIN_SECRET` value you set in your service file or environment.

### Recommended First Steps

1. **Set portal branding** — Go to **Settings** and update the portal title and subtitle.
2. **Configure pricing plans** — Edit the data rate plans (name, duration, speed, price label) to match your offerings.
3. **Generate test vouchers** — Go to **Vouchers → Generate** and create a few codes to verify the full flow.
4. **Test user flow** — Connect a phone to the hotspot, browse to any site, and confirm you land on the portal. Enter a voucher and verify internet access is granted.

